'''Colchagua Club de Deportes''' are a [[Chile]]an [[Football club]], their home town is [[San Fernando, Chile|San Fernando]] in Chile. They currently play in third division of Chilean football, [[Segunda División de Chile]]. His traditional rival is [[Club Deportivo O'Higgins|O'Higgins]].

