The '''Estonian Cyclists' Union''' or '''EJL''' (in [[Estonian language|Estonian]]: ''Eesti Jalgratturite Liit'') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Estonia]].

The EJL is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme|UEC]].

