'''[[South Korea]]''', as ''Korea'' participated at the '''[[1954 Asian Games]]''' held in the city of [[Manila]], [[Philippines]] from May 1, 1954 to May 9, 1954. The country was ranked third with eight gold medals in this edition of the [[Asian Games|Asiad]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ocasia.org/2AG.asp|title=2nd Asian Games medal tally|publisher=|accessdate=13 April 2018|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070210122609/http://www.ocasia.org/2AG.asp|archivedate=10 February 2007|df=}}</ref>
